eboat.com/blog/2026/07/chinese-scientists-develop-worlds-first-bionic-auditory-neural-interface-enabling-artificial-auditory-nerve-to-understand-sounds</link><description>《环球时报》周一从研究团队获悉，中国科学家成功研制出全球首个仿生听觉神经接口，使传统人工耳蜗从帮助用户听到声音进步到帮助用户理解所听到的内容，标志着从恢复听觉感知到重建听觉功能的重大进步。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/chinese-scientists-develop-worlds-first-bionic-auditory-neural-interface-enabling-artificial-auditory-nerve-to-understand-sounds2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Jul 2026 23:45:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/chinese-scientists-develop-worlds-first-bionic-auditory-neural-interface-enabling-artificial-auditory-nerve-to-understand-sounds</guid></item><item><title>现代物理学是否极其不连贯？根据量子信息理论，事实恰恰相反！</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/is-modern-physics-hideously-incoherent-just-the-opposite-is-true-per-quantum-information-theory</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Jul 2026 23:30:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/is-modern-physics-hideously-incoherent-just-the-opposite-is-true-per-quantum-information-theory</guid></item><item><title>宇宙不是由物质组成……而是由信息组成</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/the-universe-isnt-made-of-matter-its-made-of-information</link><description>&lt;img src="https://politepol.com/fd/NjxHZtldG2if.xml" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Jul 2026 23:15:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/the-universe-isnt-made-of-matter-its-made-of-information</guid></item><item><title>X 上的 Demis Hassabis (@demishassabis)</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/07/demis-hassabis-demishassabis-on-x</link><description>https://x.com/i/article/2076946210397552640&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/demis-hassabis-demishassabis-on-x.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 